metadata.name: Your Kisses are Blood Red but my Heart is Bleeding Blue
metadata.description:
This portrait of Rob Moir, better known to the community as "Chevy Pop" was taken in Miami during Art Basel 2021. Rob was an early leader in the Web3 arena, the people's collector and known for his outrageous humor, realism and sense of style. I believe this portrait truly captures the essence of this man's spirit.

Shot on a Leica SL2-S. 

Leica Gang Gang
metadata.Our Secret: Rob Moir is my Bastard Lover
